name: Drew Force V Men N Round Toe Leather  Athletic Sneakers
column8:
*array(['[{","numHelpful":"2","rating":4.0,"sourceURLs":["http://www.shoes.com/mens-drew-force-v-black-leather-p2_id109270"],"text":"My husband has drop foot and wears a brace. It\'s not easy to find shoes that work especially in a size 12 1/2 but these work. The straps could be longer since a brace takes up some width...they barely close securely. We had them altered at our local shoe shop.","title":"Great Looking and very orthotic friendly","username":"Linda"},{,"numHelpful":"1","rating":4.0,"sourceURLs":["http://www.shoes.com/mens-drew-force-v-black-leather-p2_id109270"],"text":"I have bad arches, and wear urtodics--- without the steel shank, shoes only last 6 -8 weeks before my feet start to pain When that happens, those shoes are done","title":"So far - so good","username":"Rol"},{"date":"2012-07-04T00:00:00Z","dateAdded":"2016-11-01T09:53:32Z",","numHelpful":"3","rating":2.0,"sourceURLs":["http://www.shoes.com/mens-drew-force-v-black-leather-p2_id109270"],"text":"The shoes were true to size and comfortable but after 4 months of wear time at work they literally came apart in all the seams. Very disappointed in the durability of the shoe.","title":"Shoes literally came apart at every seam","username":"Don\'s Show Birds"},{"date":"2011-12-18T06:00:00Z",,"numHelpful":"4","rating":5.0,"sourceURLs":["http://www.shoes.com/mens-drew-force-v-black-leather-p2_id109270"],"text":"Very comfortable for walking. I am 88 years old and have had problems with my feet for the past 20 years. I have tried a dozen different kinds of shoes and more arch supports and special innersoles than I can count and none if them even come close to the Drew Force V. This is the one and only shoe I will ever buy again. My 20 year search for the best shoe is now over! I took Online Shoes advise and ordered a half size smaller than I normanly buy and they fit perfect.","title":"Great Shoes","username":"Sore Feet"},{,"numHelpful":"4","rating":5.0,"sourceURLs":["http://www.shoes.com/mens-drew-force-v-black-leather-p2_id109270"],"text":"I wear these shoes to work, and at home. They are very comfortable. For once I have a shoe that actually fits my extra wide foot. It has great support and traction. The velcro fasteners are truly convenientand work quite well.The shoe is casual, but dressy enough to be worn to work with dress slacks. I will buy these shoes again and again.","title":"Finally a shoe that fits!","username":"Mike"}]'],
      )
